Index_i   : Inital index of the current gridlines
Index_f   : Final index of the current gridlines
Grid_opt  : Options for grid arrangement (U : Uniform, G : Geometric, H : Hyperbolic tangent)
Factor1   : Exp.(1) or Comp.(0) (for Geometric) / Exp.(1) or Comp.(0) or Symmetric(0.5) (for Hyperbolic tangent) 
