*** Grid Input Rules
1. Grid setting must be written in 'upward' order for each direction.
(e.g., gridlines from (-5.0 ~ -2.0) -> gridlines from (-2.0 ~ 0.0) is okay, but the reverse is not.)
2. The initial coordinate(index) value must be equal to the final coordinate(index) value of the previous line.
3. The first index_i must be 1 in each direction
4. The last index_f must be N_i in i-direction
5. The last coord_f subtracted by the first coord_i must be L_i for i-direction
